<h3 id="icons">Icons</h3>
<p>Use icons as complementary visual aids (see <a href="/design/icons">Icons</a>).</p>
<p>Button icons should be left-aligned (default) when:</p>
<ul>
<li>Used purely as a decorative aid (e.g. check for success).</li>
<li>Used to indicate the performance of a regressive or destructive action (e.g. left arrow for back, x for cancel).</li>
</ul>

